headline.print_headline: American Country Singer Aldean Tops Billboard Chart for Second Time
headline.main: American Country Singer Aldean Tops Billboard Chart for Second Time

lead_paragraph: Country singer Jason Aldean landed his second No. 1 record on the U.S. Billboard 200 album chart on Wednesday, leading a slew of new debuts.
